data.description: Experience luxury living in this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-full-bath home located within the award-winning Vail Unified School District. The neutral palette throughout the home provides a versatile backdrop for your personal style. Step into your own private oasis with a refreshing pool, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Bask in the breathtaking mountain views from your own balcony, offering a serene escape from the daily hustle. No rear neighbors! This home seamlessly combines comfort and style, promising an exceptional living experience. Take advantage of the seller's 3% assumable loan.
